{"type": "article", "id": 25075, "title": "轻简版黑胶唱片播放器", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:11:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160342zPTbp4DdOwtZQje8.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款非常轻巧的黑胶唱片播放器，来自意大利的设计团队 AUDIO DEVA。他们改进了原本播放器笨重的形象，将基座设计成三角形，更配合现代家居环境。而主体材料采用铝合金，减轻了播放器的重量。其中唱臂管壳的重量是 2 克，不会压坏唱片本身。产品目前在众筹，预计今年 9 月份上市，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/959799437/atmo-sferatm-platterless-turntable?ref=nav_search\">这里是众筹链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160337hUrs4DQO2NuidglK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160338z9JOh0pfwBRWgiel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160338iA7JCOhKcLpQbYHX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160339zl1BkvZFbs7QfNDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160341eQkRYzVwd2si3yGv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}